text: Steeve Selso Saint-Duc (born 8 January 2000), commonly known as Selso, is a Haitian footballer who last played for Lansing Ignite.RICHMOND KICKERS VS. LANSING IGNITE == Club career== Los Angeles declined a contract option for Saint-Duc.
